is F of B.

00:03:33.936 --> 00:03:34.769
F of B.

00:03:35.682 --> 00:03:37.112
And once again we're saying F is a

00:03:37.112 --> 00:03:38.666
continuous function.

00:03:38.666 --> 00:03:40.385
So I should be able to go from F of A

