00:04:22.953 --> 00:04:25.690
between F of A and F of B

00:04:25.690 --> 00:04:27.052
over the interval.

00:04:27.052 --> 00:04:28.921
And you see in both of these cases

00:04:28.921 --> 00:04:30.985
every interval, sorry, every

00:04:30.985 --> 00:04:33.481
every value between F of A

00:04:33.481 --> 00:04:34.985
