00:05:06.677 --> 00:05:08.888
in the closed interval from A to B

00:05:08.888 --> 00:05:11.192
for which F of C equals L.

00:05:11.192 --> 00:05:12.818
So there exists at least one C.

00:05:12.818 --> 00:05:14.233
So in this case

00:05:14.233 --> 00:05:16.321
