there's multiple candidates for C.

00:05:19.879 --> 00:05:22.143
That could be a candidate for C.

00:05:22.143 --> 00:05:23.832
That could be a C.

00:05:23.832 --> 00:05:26.422
So we could say there exists at least

00:05:26.422 --> 00:05:27.436
one number.

00:05:27.436 --> 00:05:28.269
At least

00:05:29.863 --> 00:05:32.439
one number, I'll throw that in there,

00:05:32.439 --> 00:05:34.126
at least one number C

00:05:34.126 --> 00:05:36.558
in the interval for which this is true.

00:05:36.558 --> 00:05:38.737
And, something that might amuse you

